  @prompt
    Create a full-width hero section block for a homepage, designed to combine lifestyle branding with welcoming text. The layout should be:
    üìê Layout Structure:
    Left side: Full-height background image featuring an interior/lifestyle setup (e.g., sofa, vase, curtain).
    Right side: Text overlay positioned vertically centred and horizontally aligned right, containing:
    A large heading (e.g. ‚ÄúWelcome to Honeypot‚Äù)
    Paragraph(s) of descriptive brand storytelling text
    ‚öôÔ∏è Customisation Controls:
    Upload/edit the background image
    Edit:
    Heading text
    Paragraph text (multi-line supported)
    Set text alignment (left/right/centre)
    Adjust:
    Text colour
    Text block max width
    Padding and spacing
    üñ•Ô∏è Design & Behaviour:
    Text sits on top of the image but with enough spacing and contrast to ensure readability.
    Support an optional semi-transparent background for the text box (toggleable).
    Ensure mobile responsiveness by:
    Stacking the image above the text on small screens
    Maintaining padding and readability
    üíÖ Visual Style:
